  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n*Summary*: \r\ncontact picture (custom) is not updated after user added you to his contacts in Public Chat, as well as chat header is not updated in 1-1 chat\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n7) 1-1 chat: chat header is updated;\r\n8) Public chat: can see custom user photo;\r\n\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n7) 1-1 chat: chat header is not updated;\r\n![custname](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/42618270-2a2f926e-85bd-11e8-9475-5e7d89740601.png)\r\n\r\n8) Public chat: default avatar is displayed\r\n![publ](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/4557972/42617771-7778e022-85bb-11e8-900f-65ab890f6fa9.png)\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n* Prerequisites: \r\nUser A: uses status-desktop\r\nUser B: uses status-mobile, has custom photo and username set.\r\n\r\n1) (User A) Open Status\r\n2) (User A) Click on +\r\n3) (User A) Start chat with User B, send some message\r\n4) (User A) Join to any public chat (i.e. #test)\r\n5) (User B) Open chat with User A\r\n6) (User B) Click on \"Add to contacts\"\r\n6) (User B) Send something to public chat #test\r\n7) (User A) open 1-1 chat with User B\r\n8) (User A) open #test\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: [desktop_build_11.07.2018](https://jenkins.status.im/job/status-react/job/desktop/job/manual/47/)\r\n* Operating System: Mac OSx High Sierra\r\n\r\n",
